title: Morrowind Mods.rar
description:
A collection of mods made by players for Bethesda Softworks' Elder Scrolls III: Morrowind. All mods are individually compressed within the main rar, and include their original readmes and all other files. WinRAR recommended to open, but WinZIP will be able to open most. Enjoy, Morrowind fans, and don't forget to seed!


Long live TPB!

Mods Include:
Ultimate Galleon
Farmer's Mod
Necessities of Morrowind (NoM)
Vampire Embrace
Abot's Water Life
Fliggerty's Armor Project
Fishing Academy
Building Up Uvirth's Grave (BUUG)
Indestructable's Bank mod
Pocket Pals mod collection
Ranger Tent mod
Wayfarer's Rest
Wrye Mash save game/leveled list/plugin repair tool
Better Bodies (Nude/clothed versions)
Vardenfell Druglord + Skooma Anonymous expansion
Aimeekay's PC Smithy + Clothes shop mods
Cellophane's Lovers and Legends mod
Crusaders of Tamriel mod

+ many more, 82 mods total!
